message.body: Hey! Did you get my voicemail?
Just saw it. Nice!! And absolutely. I'm going to be in the city until 7:30ish on the 5th so I could even meet you where the bus drops off. Excited to see you! :) :)
Also what in gods name happened at plenary? I keep seeing the words "special plenary" float around on fb?!
Oh right you drive. Yeah that would prob be faster, and you can park at my house.
Ill fill you in later. Should I not drive then? Is there parking near where you live?
